HotForex has emerged as the 2020 “Forex Trading Platform of the Year” at the BusinessDay 8th Annual Banks & Other Financial Institutions Awards. Established in 2010, HotForex is a registered brand name of the HF Markets Group of companies. Speaking on the award, the Country Director of HotForex in Nigeria, Ope Abiola, said “winning the award is a testament that HotForex is a Leader in Financial Trading. We dedicate this award to our loyal clients and partners who place their trust in us. This award will only spur us on to continue to provide the best possible trading environment to our clients” HotForex has already joined the ranks of the World Finance Top 100; a great honor earned for excellence in offering innovative products, outstanding customer service and unparalleled trading conditions. In just ten years, it already boasts: <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-859186" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/DSC_0662-copy-scaled.jpg" alt="" width="2560" height="1707" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/DSC_0662-copy-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/DSC_0662-copy-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/DSC_0662-copy-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/DSC_0662-copy-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/DSC_0662-copy-2048x1365.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px"> · Over 2,500,000 live accounts · 45+ industry awards HotForex clients enjoy an award-winning client-centric experience. They can diversify their portfolios with CFDs on Forex, Metals, Energies, Indices, Shares, Commodities, ETFs, DMA Stocks, Bonds or Crypto currencies. In addition, a wide range of account types, trading tools and educational resources are available for traders of all levels of experience. In ten years in the business, HotForex has displayed a continuous commitment to its core values of Honesty, Open